<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_arcade",
    "The official Half-Life demo (1999) — 3 unique levels not found in the full game, set in Black Mesa's underground labs. Real-time storytelling with no cutscenes, no chapter breaks — just you, Gordon Freeman, and a crowbar."
  )}
</p>
<.diagram_arcade_halflife class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto my-4" />
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_clock}>{dgettext("help_arcade", "About")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_arcade",
    "Released February 12, 1999 as a standalone demo for Valve's Half-Life (1998). Unlike most game demos, Uplink features levels and a scenario that do not appear in the full game — the chapters were cut during Half-Life's development and heavily revised for the demo. Fight through Black Mesa's underground labs in the aftermath of the resonance cascade, encountering headcrabs, zombies, and military soldiers."
  )}
</p>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_arcade",
    "Originally distributed as a free standalone disc in retail outlets. In November 2023, Uplink was bundled with Half-Life as part of the 25th Anniversary Update, making it officially available on Steam for the first time. This runs on Xash3D-FWGS (GoldSource reimplementation) compiled to WebAssembly."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_send}>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Controls")}</.help_h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "W / ↑")}</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Move forward")}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "S / ↓")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Move backward"
    )}
  </li>
  <li><strong>A</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Strafe left")}</li>
  <li><strong>D</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Strafe right")}</li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Mouse")}</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Aim / look")}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Left Click")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Primary fire"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Right Click")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Secondary / alt-fire"
    )}
  </li>
  <li><strong>E</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Interact")}</li>
  <li><strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Space")}</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Jump")}</li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Shift")}</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Crouch")}
  </li>
  <li><strong>R</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Reload")}</li>
  <li><strong>1–5</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Weapon category")}</li>
  <li><strong>Q</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Last weapon")}</li>
  <li><strong>F</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Flashlight")}</li>
  <li><strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Esc")}</strong> {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Menu")}</li>
</ul>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_lightbulb}>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Gameplay Tips")}</.help_h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Secondary fire is key")}</strong>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Weapons have alt-fire modes. The shotgun's double-barrel blast is devastating up close."
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Use the flashlight")}</strong> {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Dark areas hide enemies and items. Toggle with F."
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Crowbar headcrabs")}</strong>
    {dgettext("help_arcade", "— Headcrabs are weak to melee. Save bullets for tougher enemies.")}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Crouch-jump for height")}</strong>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— Hold crouch while jumping to reach higher ledges. Essential for navigation."
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Listen to scientists")}</strong>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "— NPCs give hints about what's ahead. Pay attention to their dialogue."
    )}
  </li>
</ul>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_star}>{dgettext("help_arcade", "Did You Know?")}</.help_h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "Half-Life: Uplink contains 3 levels that don't appear in the full game — they were designed exclusively for the demo from cut chapters."
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "Half-Life was almost cancelled when Valve showed it to Sierra in 1997 — the publisher thought it wasn't fun enough. Valve scrapped 12 months of work and started over."
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    {dgettext(
      "help_arcade",
      "In November 2023, Uplink was bundled with Half-Life as part of the 25th Anniversary Update, making it officially available on Steam for the first time after 24 years."
    )}
  </li>
</ul>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>{dgettext("help_arcade", "See Also")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  <.help_link topic="feature-arcade-halflife">
    {dgettext("help_arcade", "Half-Life (Arcade)")}
  </.help_link>
